@META
dir: skillsPraut/scripts/
updated: 2026-04-09
files: 1
stack: Node.js (ESM)

@EXPORTS
extract-phosphor-glyphs.mjs: CLI script — extracts icon glyphs from Phosphor CSS to JSON

@FUNCTIONS
extract-phosphor-glyphs.mjs() → void
  purpose: parse style.css → phosphor-glyphs.json
  side-effects: file (writes src/components/icons/phosphor-glyphs.json)

@PROCESSES
glyph-extraction: phosphor-icons/Fonts/regular/style.css → regex parse .ph-<name>:before → JSON map → phosphor-glyphs.json

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: phosphor-icons/Fonts/regular/style.css (input)
external: node:fs | node:path | node:url

@STANDARDS
- Run via: npm run extract-glyphs (or node scripts/extract-phosphor-glyphs.mjs)
- Output: src/components/icons/phosphor-glyphs.json
- Exits with code 1 if no glyphs extracted
